Unfortunately TF Lite doesn't support ArgMax yet. See the list of supported ops

Until it gets added, your best bet is to change your training script to avoid using ArgMax. You can also set --output_array in toco in a way that avoids the argmax node, but that might not be what you want anyway.

body:
Unfortunately TF Lite doesn't support ArgMax yet. See [the list of supported ops](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/contrib/lite/g3doc/tf_ops_compatibility.md) 

Until it gets added, your best bet is to change your training script to avoid using ArgMax. You can also set --output_array in toco in a way that avoids the argmax node, but that might not be what you want anyway.
